   [Documentation]
   ...  - create 1 appinst
   ...  - create a dme persistent connection
   ...  - update app to add autprov policy and thus spin up new appinst closer
   ...  - verify cloudlet update event is received with new cloudlet

   [Tags]  DMEPersistentConnection

